'''Sonic Free''' was a band founded by [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] teen star [[Skawn Bonduna]] near the end of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]] that was eventually banned altogether by the [[Imperial Board of Culture]]. The IBC claimed that the band's songs contained subliminal messages encouraging listeners to rebel against the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]], and imprisoned all of Sonic Free's members, though Skawn was able to escape. The other members were killed in a prison brawl.

